   6:../.././hal//stm32f3/stm32f3xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:../.././hal//stm32f3/stm32f3xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *          functionalities of the General Purpose Input/Output (GPIO) peripheral:
   8:../.././hal//stm32f3/stm32f3xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + Initialization and de-initialization functions
   9:../.././hal//stm32f3/stm32f3xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *           + IO operation functions
  10:../.././hal//stm32f3/stm32f3xx_hal_gpio.c ****   *
